      "writtenOn": "2021-03-31T20:38:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t have strong opinion.\n\nMy thinking was that reloading is cheap, as it\u0027ll likely hitting Redis.\nExtra state means potentially more things to be out of sync.\nIn PM, I didn\u0027t have a choice -- re-loading all CLs even from Redis every time is way too expensive. OTOH, here it\u0027s bearable.\n\nDeferring to you.",
